text:
Como embaixador da Liga Portuguesa Contra o Cancro, trago-vos um pedido muito especial. Ontem iniciou-se o Peditório Nacional, promovido pela LPCC.

Até dia 5 de novembro, juntem-se a nós e façam parte desta equipa! Com apenas um donativo estão a ajudar na luta contra o cancro.

Contra o cancro todos contam!

➡️ Saibam como apoiar esta causa em: www.ligacontracancro.pt/donativos

#LigaContraCancro #Peditorio #oquenosLIGA

As an ambassador of the Portuguese League Against Cancer, I bring you a very special request. Yesterday, the National Pediatrician, powered by the LPCC, started.

Until November 5th, come join us and be a part of this team! With just one donation you are helping fight cancer.

Against cancer everyone counts!

➡️ Learn how to support this cause at: www.ligacontracancro.pt/donativos

#LigaContraCancro #Peditorio #oquenosLIGA

Liga Portuguesa Contra o Cancro
25 October at 15:52 ·

Ao participar no Peditório Nacional com um donativo está a apoiar:
➡️ o doente oncológico e cuidadores;
➡️ a promoção da saúde;
➡️ a prevenção do cancro;
➡️estímulo à formação e investigação em oncologia.

Ninguém consegue fazer tudo sozinho. Junte-se à Liga Portuguesa Contra o Cancro!

Saiba como apoiar esta causa em: www.ligacontracancro.pt/donativos

#LigaContraCancro #Peditorio #oquenosLIGA

By participating in the National Pediatrician with a donation you're supporting:
➡️ the oncology patient and caregivers;
➡️ the promotion of health;
➡️ cancer prevention;
➡️ Encouragement for training and research in oncology.

No one can do it all alone. Join the Portuguese League Against Cancer!

Learn how you can support this cause at: www.ligacontracancro.pt/donativos

#LigaContraCancro #Peditorio #oquenosLIGA

text:
7 YEARS OF GOOD VIBES! Let’s celebrate the 7th anniversary of Pestana CR7 Lifestyle Hotels!

The journey began with a vision, team spirit and a dream by myself and Dionisio Pestana - to create not just hotels, but unforgettable experiences across the globe for urban explorers.

From the captivating shores of Funchal to the vibrant streets of Lisbon. The cosmopolitan allure of Madrid to the enchanting essence of New York and of course the magic of Marrakech. Our hotels have become more than just a place to stay, but a destination for inspiration!

Stay tuned for exciting anniversary surprises and celebration throughout the year 🎁🎈

Discover more at pestanacr7.com and Pestana CR7

#PestanaCR7 #PCR7GoodVibes
